      "content": "it's not really about a break though. i've done the rest part. it just feels like the itinerary is finished. like, i've checked all the boxes and now i'm just standing at the edge of the cliff looking at the horizon, and the only thing that makes sense is just... stopping. being done. why keep walking when there's nowhere else to go?",
